     C                     MOVE ALKNO     A5KNO
     C                     MOVE ALROUT    A5ROUT
     C                     MOVE ALUKEI    A5UKEI
     C                     MOVE ALRESV    A5RESV
     C* BOTTOM KANBAN (IN-HOUSE)
